{
  "stem": "18654.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 103.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he tried to get in, and he couldn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then somebody said to him, wear a kippah next time you go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he managed to get in to the diamond trade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The diamond trade was flourishing at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But soon afterwards it became very erratic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were times when he had no work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That meant no money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not-- it's not again like now, if you didn't work, you didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it became really bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And eventually it became so bad that he decided-- I think the factory closed down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And through a distant-- very, very distant relative that I've mentioned before, we found another job-- he found another job.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was something completely different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he made a go of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And through this job, he met a-- a young man from Israel who was working and living here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they started a business which flourished, and became a very good business.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did, funnily enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When-- I had to get permission to get married.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I was underage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had to go to Woburn House to get permission.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said to me, you are going to get 50 pounds, which was a fortune as far as I was concerned in 1949.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, why?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where do I get-- why will I get 50 pounds?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, they told me that a man had died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He must be a fantastic man, anonymous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anonymously, he wouldn't give his-- I never knew his name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had left a sum of money to be given to any refugee girl who was an orphan, 50 pounds at a time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I got the last 50 pounds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was rich.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had 50 pounds when I married.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
